{"tid":2372710,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[戰鬥民族] 初步臨床測試顯示 俄羅斯第二款疫苗有效性達100%","createTime":"2021-01-20T02:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T07:42:04.000Z","uid":35270,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9d45d385e3fbf6d8bf6893eef9b4368d5f4655","tid":2372710,"uid":35270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"初步臨床測試顯示，俄羅斯第二款準備註冊的2019冠狀病毒候選疫苗EpiVacCorona的有效性高達100%。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯經貿與衛生調查局告訴當地媒體，這款疫苗完成了第一和第二階段的測試，並將進入第三階段的大規模測試，參與測試的人有數千名。<br />\n<br />\n第一和第二階段測試主要是測試疫苗的安全性、副作用和免疫原性，參與測試的有100人，年齡介於18到60歲。<br />\n<br />\n這款疫苗是由俄羅斯國家病毒學與生物技術研究中心開發的。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯副總理塔季揚娜&middot;戈利科娃說，當局計畫3月起為大批民眾注射這款疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/world/article/russia-covid-vaccine-1369311?fbclid=IwAR2VXR_F8AyknFo0t-Zj9DSS0KRi-__7IVBrloS39l2468w50voFvBCiOEo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Farticle%2Frussia-covid-vaccine-1369311%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2VXR_F8AyknFo0t-Zj9DSS0KRi-__7IVBrloS39l2468w50voFvBCiOEo&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmepgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=237f96d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/world/article/russia-covid-vaccine-1369311?fbclid=IwAR2VXR_F8AyknFo0t-Zj9DSS0KRi-__7IVBrloS39l2468w50voFvBCiOEo</a>"},{"pid":"279a4b2788c6f1394d294a9bc91c8da50df96a0e","tid":2372710,"uid":206241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abbcd61177e695275d0a4c9b4d822de7d0baefb","tid":2372710,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"俄佬世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a81d70e3bd9ef66dccd4422616758b3d2a4b4b1","tid":2372710,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"係個疫苗有效定俄佬本身就&gt;武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},